Package: whisper-finetuning-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-pyqt6, python3-pyqt6.qtmultimedia, python3-numpy, python3-requests, python3-dotenv
Description: Whisper Fine-Tuning Data Collection Tool
 A PyQt6 desktop application for collecting speech-to-text training data.
 Records audio samples paired with text prompts to create datasets for
 fine-tuning Whisper and other speech recognition models.
 .
 Features include:
  - Multiple text generation styles
  - Hebrew-English term support
  - Technical/developer terminology
  - Audio recording with configurable microphone
  - Dataset management and export
